#: budgie-welcome:452
msgid "Open the menu and search for 'Install RELEASE'"
msgstr "Dobrissètz lo menú e cercatz « Installar RELEASE »"

#: budgie-welcome:504
msgid ""
"Seems that GNOME Software is not installed. If this problem persists even "
"after installing GNOME Software, please contact us with following error "
"message"
msgstr ""
"Sembla que GNOME Software es pas installat. Se lo problèma persistís aprèp "
"l’installacion de GNOME Software, contactatz-nos amb lo messatge d’error "
"seguent "

#: budgie-welcome:514
msgid ""
"Seems that App Center is not installed. If this problem persists even after "
"installing App Center, please contact us with following error message"
msgstr ""
"Sembla que lo Centre d’aplicacions es pas installat. Se lo problèma "
"persistís e mai aprèp aver installat App Center, contactatz-nos amb lo "
"messatge d'error seguent"

#: budgie-welcome:763
msgid "Following tasks are in progress"
msgstr "Los prètzfaches seguents son en cors"

#: budgie-welcome:770 budgie-welcome:2003 budgie-welcome:2020
#: budgie-welcome:2048 budgie-welcome:2054 budgie-welcome:2568
msgid "Budgie Welcome"
msgstr "Benvenguda de Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:774
msgid "Budgie Desktop"
msgstr "Burèu Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:902
msgid ""
"The following third-party repositories need to be added to complete the "
"installation:"
msgstr ""
"Los repertòris tèrces seguents an d’èsser apondut per acabar l’installacion :"

#: budgie-welcome:955 budgie-welcome:977
msgid ""
"Third-Party repositories and their packages are not supported by Ubuntu. You "
"should only continue if you trust the maintainers of these repositories."
msgstr ""
"Los depaus tèrces e lors paquets son pas preses en carga per Ubuntu. "
"Deuriatz contunhar solament se fasètz fisança als manteneires d'aquestes "
"depaus."

#: budgie-welcome:958 budgie-welcome:980
msgid "Continue with the installation?"
msgstr "Contunhar l’installacion ?"

#: budgie-welcome:964 budgie-welcome:986
msgid "Third-Party Repositories"
msgstr "Repertòris tèrces"

#: budgie-welcome:975
msgid ""
"One or more packages need to be installed from a third-party repository that "
"you have previously added."
msgstr ""
"Un o mantun paquet devon èsser installats a partir d'un depaus tèrç qu'avètz "
"apondut precedentament."

#: budgie-welcome:1297
msgid "Welcome App"
msgstr "Aplicacion de benvenguda"

#: budgie-welcome:1671
msgid "Could not gather data."
msgstr "Recuperacion de las donada impossibla."

#: budgie-welcome:1751
msgid "GB"
msgstr "Go"

#: budgie-welcome:1752
msgid "GiB"
msgstr "Gio"

#: budgie-welcome:1753
msgid "MB"
msgstr "Mo"

#: budgie-welcome:1754
msgid "MiB"
msgstr "Mio"

#: budgie-welcome:2005
msgid ""
"This snap is running on a distro that is unrecognized or on a development "
"release of Ubuntu that has not yet received its snap configuration.  Full "
"snap capabilities are unlikely to work."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste snap s'executa sus una distribucion qu'es pas reconeguda o sus una "
"version de desvolopament d'Ubuntu qu'a pas encara recebut sa configuracion "
"snap. Es pauc probable que las foncionalitats complètas de snap foncionen."

#: budgie-welcome:2022
msgid ""
"This snap is running on version of budgie desktop that is no longer "
"supported. Please upgrade to a supported version of the distro."
msgstr ""
"Aqueste snap s'executa sus una version de budgie desktop qu'es pas mai presa "
"en carga. Volgatz metre a nivèl cap a una version presa en carga de la "
"distribucion."

#: budgie-welcome:2069
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Estat "

#: budgie-welcome:2172
msgid " is in progress. Please wait for it to complete"
msgstr "es en cors. Esperatz qu’acabe"

#: budgie-welcome:2569
msgid "Find out about your operating system"
msgstr "Ne saber mai sus vòstre sistèma operatiu"

#: budgie-welcome:2571
msgid "Budgie Makeovers & Layouts"
msgstr "Transformacions e ajustaments de Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:2572
msgid "Give the desktop a makeover with new themes, icons, fonts & layouts"
msgstr "Renovatz lo burèu amb de tèmas, icònas, poliças e agençaments novèls"

#: budgie-welcome:2574
msgid "Budgie Extras"
msgstr "Budgie Extras"

#: budgie-welcome:2575
msgid ""
"Customize the desktop with applets and mini-applications to provide extra "
"capabilities"
msgstr ""
"Personalizatz lo burèu amb d’applets e de mini aplicacions per fornir mai de "
"capacitats"

#: budgie-welcome:2578
msgid "Budgie Discourse"
msgstr "Discourse de Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:2579
msgid "Be part of the Ubuntu Budgie Community"
msgstr "Formatz part de la comunautat Ubuntu Budgie"
